T1  - Aggregate Fluctuations with National and International Returns to Scale*
AU  - Head, Allen C.
Y1  - 2002/11/01
PY  - 2002
DA  - 2002/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/1468-2354.t01-1-00050
T2  - International Economic Review
